# ================== Ester Hybrid Search — ENV presety (primer) ==================
# A/B-slot gibridnogo poiska:
#   A - pastnrougne: use the current dense search as is.
#   B - ensemble: source (BM25/hierarchical) + dense (vector) with linear mixing.
HYBRID_SEARCH_AB=A

# All dance in the ensemble (0..1). 0.55 - a dense layer is a little more important than the source.
HYBRID_ALPHA=0.55

# How many candidates to take from the source search to rank the Dense?
HYBRID_COARSE_LIMIT=50

# Mosty:
# - Yavnyy: (Infoteoriya ↔ Inzheneriya) upravlenie ensemble bez pravki koda.
# - Skrytyy #1: (Kibernetika ↔ Resursy) ogranichenie pula kandidatov.
# - Skrytyy #2: (Memory ↔ Poisk) stabilnost kontraktov dlya RAG.

# Earthly paragraph: these are “regulators on the mixer” - which flow is considered the main one and how many candidates to mix.

# c=a+b
